{"tid":1369131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎]聽日真係唔好勇武","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:49:10.000Z","uid":53361,"like":45,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"33d3bd3d07151baf85f7eb4a72153484fdb07dca","tid":1369131,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:35:09.000Z","msg":"屌哂你地老母<br />\n咪撚再係到分化<br />\n<br />\n勇武既定義唔係衝擊<br />\n只係企前排就係勇武<br />\n幫你擋彈既就係勇武<br />\n擋住黑警比和理非走先就係勇武<br />\n比人打會還擊自衛就係勇武<br />\n<br />\n咪再係度帶風向話勇武會主動出擊好似黑幫咁打人<br />\n勇武都係和理非既一部分<br />\n只係佢地比你地有勇氣用武力制暴<br />\n唔好再係到改變勇武既形象<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n全部同我入元朗行街打卡捉Pokemon<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"3929854e14142f4fcc98372dbc0636271d4304cc","tid":1369131,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89bd3f9b3b476029e1648560605a57300eccb23","tid":1369131,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d20401c39f737b3690dd4465f7e956548da99c","tid":1369131,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8e9d1b13a6822f109283b9ecd545258550b499d4","tid":1369131,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"df6d13031cfe330d114f9b0eb6c29b57540884d8","tid":1369131,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:38:58.000Z","msg":"只做反擊，不做主動攻擊，做正義一方"},{"pid":"9d9181ef9ff2a8ddb0016719dc608572a21679d9","tid":1369131,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfba43401ab4b5bed7d214984b2a3584163a80b","tid":1369131,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"d人好鍾意妖魔化勇武"},{"pid":"434f80edf95f53a498153eb78f55b6075dd79d4c","tid":1369131,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d800c5687d68dc963055eaef6f31ae60c440ca","tid":1369131,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"大家都眼目近日元朗新聞<br />\n咁都可以指麇為那 癲倒是非<br />\n<br />\n大家自問一下，<br />\n做下心理功課，諗下應對，<br />\n以免入村變入侵，又有人保家衛國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 有人沖入，你跟唔跟<br />\n2. 村入面有人撩你，你沖唔沖<br />\n3. 有人打完手足，龜入村，你沖唔沖<br />\n4. 有人捉左手足入村，救唔救！<br />\n5. 警察三面圍迫，焗你入村<br />\n6. 圍村要交人，圍幾耐，點進行下一步<br />\n7. 如果非法遊行被捉，點做？<br />\n<br />\n一定要記者<br />\n拍片紀錄係最強大武器<br />\n<br />\n一定要先禮後兵<br />\n有聲公講清楚發生咩事，唔要得口號。<br />\n就算手捉被人捉左入村！"},{"pid":"3d040b45b119c235f5986c71b9ee5c30d1ae9178","tid":1369131,"uid":35632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43673c0692dab6f88443c7a09cc7bd904f665ea2","tid":1369131,"uid":199834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"唔係話要打不還手 但千萬不能放火<br />\n聽日已經比左機會佢地借刀殺人 <br />\n無謂送埋個正當理由比佢地攻擊我地性命"},{"pid":"c843aee0b1416743f8770bfb71f508eb0409f37b","tid":1369131,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6a473407298d48fc2acaab08e07125778ccb03","tid":1369131,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}